data.description:
Welcome to this inviting home! Featuring hardwood floors throughout, a kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and four spacious bedrooms including a primary suite on the upper level, it offers style, functionality and comfort. Enjoy the enclosed patio year round and a partially finished basement for extra space. Fresh paint inside and carpet pulled up to reveal the gorgeous hardwood this home is move-in ready. Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood close to schools, shopping and dining. Updated HVAC, water heater and more! Schedule a showing today!
https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=79muQQvm4GH
